description: Here we finish off Tetrachords and check out part of a Bud Powell solo involving some great use of Tetrachords. Note that Powell is playing Indiana in it's original key of F concert. Most Boppers at the time were playing this song in Ab concert.
title: HTPB 5: Bud Powell and Tetrachords
